data.title: Cohocton, NY
data.meta_description: See what it's like to live in Cohocton, NY. Explore reviews and statistics on crime, real estate, and cost of living.
data.text: Cohocton is a rural community located in Upstate New York. This town covers a relatively large area but has a small population. The people are friendly and and this is a great place to live and raise a family. Cohocton is primarily a farming community but does have a post office, grocery store, and a number of merchants that have businesses in and around the village. The Cohocton River is a stocked trout stream with numerous places to fish with public access. Country living is great and the area is full of the beauty of trees, streams, and hill sides.
